From: OpenAI Codex <codex@openai.com>
Subject: [PATCH] net: ethernet: freescale: dpaa: add Goal 1 flowtable base

Add the first Goal 1 DPAA flowtable patch with these constraints:

- bind to the stock `TC_SETUP_FT` flowtable hook
- compile accepted stock flowtable rules into driver-owned records
- reject unsupported shapes explicitly with per-reason counters
- expose delayed stats and install/reject visibility
- leave the RX/TX datapath untouched

This intentionally does not add any skb surgery, reinjection path, or
FMAN-resident execution. It establishes the install-time contract and
driver-owned state needed for later Goal 1 execution work.

